      • getTile

        public void getTile(int x,
                    int y,
                    int zoom,
                    GetDataListener<byte[]> callback)
        Gets the tile at the specified x, y and zoom. Once the tile has been loaded, the specified callback will be called with the tile image or an error if the image failed to load. The tile image will be null when no image is available for the specified location.
        Parameters:
        x - The x-coordinate of the tile (column)
        y - The y-coordinate of the tile (row)
        zoom - The zoom level of the tile
        callback - The callback will be called once the bitmap has been loaded
